answers.body_markdown:
Angular template requires a closing tag. Opened `&lt;app-comp-1&gt;` hides contents that follow.

Try below.

```
&lt;h1&gt;Hello World&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;app-comp-1&gt;&lt;/app-comp-1&gt;
&lt;app-comp-2&gt;&lt;/app-comp-2&gt;
```

